b'Bobunemimimmi Specials': b'The official website for the Pop Team Epic anime announced on Monday that the series\' Bobunemimimmi (Bob Epic Team) segments will be compiled into a standalone Blu-ray Disc release. The release will include all 22 previously released segments by the production team AC-bu, plus two new segments, a "high speed kamishibai (paper theater) collection" of the "Hellshake Yano" segment, and original stickers.\n\n(Source: ANN)'
